<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<title>Business Inquiry Received - CodeSmith InfoSoft</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
	style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Georgia', 'Segoe UI','Segoe UI', sans-serif;">
	<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding: 40px 0; background-color: #f4f6f9;">
		<tr>
			<td align="center">
				<table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
					style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden;">

					<!-- Header -->
					<div style="text-align: center;">
						<img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/code_smith.png" alt="CodeSmith InfoSoft Logo" />
					</div>

					<!-- Body -->
					<tr>
						<td style="padding: 50px 40px; color: #333;">
							<h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 30px;">Thank You for Reaching Out!</h2>
							<p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hi <strong>
									<%= data.fullName %>
								</strong>,</p>

							<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
								We’ve successfully received your business inquiry and we’re thrilled about your interest
								in <strong>CodeSmith InfoSoft</strong>. Our dedicated team is currently reviewing the
								details you provided, and you can expect a response from us within the next 24 hours.
							</p>

							<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
								In the meantime, we encourage you to explore our past projects, services, and client
								testimonials to learn more about how we’ve helped businesses like yours thrive in the
								digital world.
							</p>

							<hr style="border: none; height: 1px; background-color: #e1e1e1; margin: 30px 0;" />

							<h3 style="font-size: 18px; color: #273974; margin-bottom: 15px;">Here is a detailed summary
								of the information you submitted:</h3>

							<!-- Inquiry Table -->
							<table width="100%" cellpadding="12" cellspacing="0"
								style="border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px;">
								<tr style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
									<td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Name:</td>
									<td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
										<%= data.fullName %>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Email:</td>
									<td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
										<%= data.email %>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Phone:</td>
									<td style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
										<%= data.mobile %>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align: top;">Message:</td>
									<td>
										<%= data.message %>
									</td>
								</tr>
							</table>

							<!-- CTA -->
							<div style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
								<p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
									Want to know more about how we can help your business grow with powerful digital
									solutions?
								</p>

								<a href="https://codesmithinfosoft.com" target="_blank"
									style="display: inline-block; background-color: #119448; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 40px; text-decoration: none;">
									<img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/web.png" alt="Website Icon" width="18"
										height="18" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;" />
									<strong style="font-weight: 600;">Visit Our Website</strong>
								</a>
							</div>

							<p style="font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 0;">
								Thanks again for reaching out. We look forward to the opportunity of working with
								you.<br />
								<br />
								&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Best regards,<br />
								<strong>Team CodeSmith InfoSoft</strong>
							</p>
						</td>
					</tr>

					<!-- Footer -->
					<tr style="background-color: #273974;">
						<td align="center" style="color: #fff;">
							<div style="padding: 20px 0;">
								<p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px;">&copy; 2021 CodeSmith InfoSoft. All rights
									reserved.</p>
								<a href="https://www.instagram.com/codesmithinfosoft" target="_blank"
									style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
									<img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/insta.png" alt="Instagram" width="24"
										style="display: block;" />
								</a>
								<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/codesmithinfosoftllp" target="_blank"
									style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
									<img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/linkedin.png" alt="LinkedIn" width="24"
										style="display: block;" />
								</a>
								<a href="https://x.com/CodeSmithSHG" target="_blank"
									style="margin: 0 8px; display: inline-block;">
									<img src="<%= data.base_URL %>/assets/twitter.png" alt="X" width="24"
										style="display: block;" />
								</a>
							</div>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>

</html>